CIBC                      169 (221)    10.6 (13.5)   0.50 (0.71)
Bank of Montreal          155 (164)    12.5 (15.1)   0.56 (0.65)
Bank of Nova Scotia       165 (174)    13.9 (17)     0.65 (0.77)
Toronto-Dominion            1 (115)    -0.7 (9.6)       0 (0.66)
