<BYLINE>
   By ROLAND RUDD
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
HONGKONG LAND'S growing influence over Trafalgar House has been underlined
with the disclosure that the UK-based construction and engineering group is
to open a corporate office in Hong Kong.
It will be run by Mr John Fletcher, a senior director who has been involved
in most of the group's projects over the past decade.
