and is proposing to sub-underwrite the issue. The result will be that he
will control between 10 per cent and 27.5 per cent of the enlarged equity.
Turnover for the year was Pounds 3.96m (Pounds 3.99m). The pre-tax loss was
after exceptional costs of Pounds 181,000. Losses per share were 4.1p
(earnings 2p).
