FT  04 MAR 93 / World Stock Markets: Mexico
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
MEXICO saw a surge in activity yesterday as shares strengthened on
expectations of stable interest rates and renewed foreign demand for stocks.
The IPC index closed 22.56 ahead at 1,612.99. Technical analysts said the
